creator: Gesplan
descriptionHtml:
Tenerife ON is the official app of the Tenerife Island Council, providing all the information you need to enjoy outdoor leisure activities on the island. Here you will find a vast network of hiking, cycling and horse riding trails, recreational areas, camping areas and visitor centres, all within the Protected Natural Areas of Tenerife.

Whether you are a resident or a visitor, you will enjoy nature more safely with this single app on your mobile device, even when you have no reception.

You will also receive alerts and updates on the current state of routes and facilities, advice on best practices in nature, and information of interest on permits and authorisations. This app is the go-to resource for practising and protecting outdoor pursuits on the island.
descriptionShort: The official outdoor recreation guide from the Tenerife Island Council.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- The timetable icon in the camping areas is removed.

- Added button to accept selection when filtering itineraries/equipment.

- Removed zoom in and zoom out buttons on interactive map, added new button showing full legend.

- Show incidents on the map of the itinerary zone.

- Events are shown on the map of an itinerary card.
